(a_{n+1})^2 - a_{n+1} + a_{n} = 0
a_0\neq 0
a_{n+1}
a_{n+1}=\frac 12 (1 \pm \sqrt{1-4a_n})
a_n \gt \frac 14
a_{n+1}
(a_{n+1}-1/2)^2 = a_{n+1}^2-a_{n+1}+1/4 = -a_n+1/4 = -(a_n-1/2)-1/2+1/4 = -(a_n-1/2)-1/4 
b_n = a_n-1/2
b_{n+1}^2 = -b_n-1/4
b_n > -1/4
b_n \to L
L^2+L+1/4 = 0
(L+1/2)^2 = 0
L=-1/2
a_n \to 0
